        This method creates a technical assistant, which has some attributes of an employee and a coach pre: The user has to enter a name, id, salary, status and years of experience, their professional experience as a player or not and an expertise post: The tehnical assistant has been saved.
        Parameters:
        name - it is the name of the technical assitant. name != null
        id - it is the identification of the technical assitant. id > 0
        salary - it is the salary of the technical assitant. salary != null
        status - it is the status of the technical assitant. status = active or inactive
        experience - it is the years of experience of the technical assitant. experience != null
        professionalExperience - it is used to know if the technical assistant was a player or not before. professionalExperience = player or not player
        expertise - it is the expertise of the technical assistant. 1 < expertise < 4
